# Benchmark data lives in amptimal/surge-bench (not in this repo).
# Historically the root ``/benchmarks/`` directory was used for symlinks
# into that data. It is now a first-class source directory for
# per-market harness code (``benchmarks/<market>/``); dataset caches
# live under ``target/benchmarks/`` and are covered by the ``target/``
# rule already.
/pyproject.toml

# Test data lives in amptimal/surge-bench (copy instances/ -> tests/data/ to run tests)
/tests/data
/docs/notebooks/execution_report.json

